                    <span>VRML nowadays is a powerful tool to comunicate in a visual form to thowsands of web users. The way the authors wrote this book really motivates the reader to start a journey into the VRML standard. No deep CG  knowledge is needed to understand the contents.  Great job !</span>
                  
              
